  "description": [
    "CEDARVILLE Cedarville May 27The Knights of Pythias Lodge attended services at the Baptist Church Sunday night and a large percentage of the lodge members were present A specially prepared sermon also music for the occasion was enjoyed immensely A large number of Cedarville people went to Bridgeton Monday to see the President and hear his address Mrs E H Starkey was a Newport visitor Wednesday Cedarville High School closes today and as the weather is decidedly warm they are very pleased Strawberry packing in the factory is expected to start the last of this week The strawberry pickers are arriving here by the car loads and each day brings new crowds of Italians ready for work and the station at this time is a lively place Mr Lewis Waddington was a Cedar vine visitor in his automobile here Sunday Mrs Harry Stanton was a shopper in Bridgeton recently Cedarville May 31A large number of young folks of Cedarville including the high school class enjoyed a straw ride to Fortescue on Thursday and returned late in the evening thereby enjoying the full day in its beauty Mrs Stanton Bateman spent a day i at Fortescue recently Mrs Robert Birch was a"
